宿舍自殺，唔知啲室友點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"檢警調查，昨天陸籍男學生突然失聯，校方獲報後不敢大意，隨即前往思源街宿舍找人，並通報警消協助破門，這才發現男學生陳屍房間，警方立刻封鎖現場採證，並通知親戚到場指認。"},{"pid":"35a6d8528fc59a7b7e51b08b1f2ca18eac3dc656","tid":2283004,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:39:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=846872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D846872&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BynWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=a03f64bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D846872&h=03b52fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=846872</a>"},{"pid":"89521fda81644b16ce90d4ae48a1577a57f9e29c","tid":2283004,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9075f26a79819d392620bc5b92e35c7823a32cb0","tid":2283004,"uid":245849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"睡眠不足自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"吳男在遺書中提到，最近睡不好、心情不佳，並交代家人妥善處理個人物品及筆電。"},{"pid":"517e5ae5727c4176ebc689ebb4a32acc542f1e6b","tid":2283004,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f234b9255c417a2800fb0ce7dbe762a79b76c720","tid":2283004,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c18f4c29a94b1d581ade6398ebd93dd344d00c9","tid":2283004,"uid":67816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:56:31.000Z","msg"